author: Charles S
title: A Convenient Inn near SFO
text: The El Rancho Inn is convenient place to stay and is located in Millbrae approximately 1 mile from the airport. It has a shuttle pickup every 20 minutes from and to the airport. The restaurant, Terrace Room, also offers good menu selection and the food tasted good. The staff are friendly and courteous.
